#. type=text
#. Strings like @fields.xxx and @results.yyy should not be translated. 
msgctxt "text"
msgid "👑 Using toys or puppets, role-play scenarios where a stranger approaches. Ask @fields.child_nickname what the toy should do. Girls and boys find it less scary to pretend that someone else is in danger. "
